 \'\'chǎo\'\' (Chinese for \'\'{{wp|stir frying}}\'\') and 豚 \'\'buta\'\' (pig) or ブー \'\'bū\'\' (oink).\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=Fire|type2=Fighting\n|ja=チャオブー \'\'Chaoboo\'\'|jameaning=From {{tt|超 \'\'chāo\'\'|Chinese for super}} or {{tt|炒 \'\'chǎo\'\'|Chinese for stir frying}} and {{tt|豚 \'\'buta\'\'|pig}} or {{tt|ブー \'\'bū\'\'|oink}}\n|de=Ferkokel|demeaning=From \'\'{{tt|Ferkel|piglet}}\'\' and \'\'{{tt|kokeln|to char}}\'\'\n|fr=Grotichon|frmeaning=From \'\'{{tt|gros|fat}}\'\', \'\'{{tt|rôti|roasted}}\'\', and \'\'{{tt|cochon|pig}}\'\'\n|es=Pignite|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|it=Pignite|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=차오꿀 \'\'Chaokkul\'\'|komeaning=From {{tt|超 \'\'chāo\'\'|Chinese for \'super\'}} or {{tt|炒 \'\'chǎo\'\'|Chinese for \'stir frying\'}} and {{tt|꿀꿀 \'\'kkul-kkul\'\'|onomatopoeia for oinking}}\n|zh_cmn=炒炒豬 / 炒炒猪 \'\'Chǎochǎozhū\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=From {{tt|炒 \'\'chǎo\'\'|stir-fry}} and {{tt|豬 \'\'zhū\'\'|pig}}.\n|ru=Пигнайт \'\'Pignayt\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name\n}}\n<br clear="left">\n\n==Related articles==\n* [[Ash\'s Pignite]]\n* [[Bianca\'s Emboar|Bianca\'s Pignite]]\n* [[Nite]]\n* [[Shin\'s Pignite]]\n* [[Starter Pokémon]]\n<!--\n==Notes==\n<references />-->\n\n==External links==\n\n{{-}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Fire|type2=Fighting}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Fire|prevnum=498|prev=Tepig|nextnum=500|next=Emboar}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Ferkokel]]\n[[es:Pignite]]\n[[fr:Grotichon]]\n[[it:Pignite]]\n[[ja:チャオブー]]\n[[zh:炒炒猪]]'}